## Escalation guidance

- Simple tasks (formatting, extraction, small fixes): Light tier or Composer 2.
- Standard tasks (feature implementation, debugging): Sonnet 4.5+ or Codex 5.2+.
- Hard problems (architecture, multi-file refactoring, complex reasoning): Opus 4.6+ or Codex 5.3.
- When escalating: name the specific model in the prompt to the operator.
